@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_brqvwe(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((0.50 + wp.cos(tmp + 0.85)) + wp.cos(tmp))
    v1 = tmp
    v2 = tmp
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.abs((v0 + 0.20 - v1 + 0.24)))
    v2 = wp.sin((tmp * (v2 + 0.71 + tmp + 0.90)))
    v2 = v0
    v0 = 0.09
    data[tid] = v0
